<D>__{yeah.}
<C>__{pike}
<D>__{god! unbelievable. vampires.}
<A>__{buffy hands pike the water and they move back into the living room. pike curls up in an armchair by the window. buffy begins stripping off her bloody clothes, leaving on a tank top and jeans.}
<C>__{buffy}
<D>__{you had a car full of stuff. were you leaving?}
