<C>__{pike}
<D>__{well, i've always wanted to see oxnard.}
<A>__{as buffy strips down to her tank top, she notices a gash on her arm. it's not bleeding much any more, but it's fairly impressive. pike jumps up to help as she pats it down with her shirt.}
<C>__{pike}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{hey, jeez are you okay? you need a hand?}
