<D>__{it's nothing. it doesn't hurt.}
<A>__{pike looks at her a moment as she wraps her shirt around it.}
<C>__{pike}
<P>__{(almost awed)}
<D>__{who are you?}
<A>__{buffy doesn't look up. the questions seems to upset her a great deal. she even fights back tears.}
<C>__{pike}
<P>__{(continuing)}
<D>__{i'm sorry, i just mean... well you seemed like such a flake. but, in a good way! i can just keep talking till you strike me dead, or...}
