<C>__{pike}
<D>__{i know. my guidance counselor never mentioned anything about vampires. 'prison' came up a few times, but nothing about undead.}
<C>__{buffy}
<D>__{it's weird. i went back to my old grade school once, to the playground i used to hang out there all the time, playing on the swings and stuff... i went back and it was so tiny, the whole place. i couldn't even fit on the swings. everything just looked so small.}
<P>__{(collects herself)}
<D>__{i'm sorry. i'm babbling.}
